{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "ikibisnis-collection-v3",
    "name": "IkiBisnis — Role & User Management API",
    "description": "Koleksi lengkap Role & User Management API dengan JWT Auth.\n\n**Base URL:** `{{base_url}}/api/v1`\n\n**Cara pakai:**\n1. Set variable `base_url` → `http://localhost:3001`\n2. Jalankan **🔐 Auth → Login** → `access_token` otomatis tersimpan\n3. Jalankan **Create Role** → `role_id` otomatis tersimpan\n4. Jalankan **Create User** → `user_id` otomatis tersimpan\n\n**Semua endpoint Role & User membutuhkan Bearer Token dari Login.**",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:3001",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "access_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "JWT Bearer token — otomatis terisi setelah Login dijalankan"
    },
    {
      "key": "role_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "UUID role — otomatis terisi setelah Create Role dijalankan"
    },
    {
      "key": "user_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "UUID user — otomatis terisi setelah Create User dijalankan"
    }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{access_token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "🔐 Auth",
      "description": "Endpoint autentikasi. Jalankan **Login** terlebih dahulu agar `access_token` tersimpan otomatis.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.success && res.data && res.data.accessToken) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('access_token', res.data.accessToken);",
                  "    console.log('✅ access_token tersimpan:', res.data.accessToken.slice(0,40) + '...');",
                  "}",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Response success true', () => pm.expect(res.success).to.be.true);",
                  "pm.test('Message login berhasil', () => pm.expect(res.message).to.eql('Login berhasil'));",
                  "pm.test('Data memiliki accessToken', () => pm.expect(res.data).to.have.property('accessToken'));",
                  "pm.test('Data memiliki expiresIn', () => pm.expect(res.data).to.have.property('expiresIn'));",
                  "pm.test('Data memiliki user', () => pm.expect(res.data).to.have.property('user'));",
                  "pm.test('User memiliki id', () => pm.expect(res.data.user).to.have.property('id'));",
                  "pm.test('User isActive true', () => pm.expect(res.data.user.isActive).to.be.true);",
                  "pm.test('User memiliki permissions array', () => {",
                  "    pm.expect(res.data.user.permissions).to.be.an('array');",
                  "    pm.expect(res.data.user.permissions.length).to.be.above(0);",
                  "});",
                  "pm.test('Setiap permission punya feature & actions', () => {",
                  "    res.data.user.permissions.forEach(p => {",
                  "        pm.expect(p).to.have.property('feature');",
                  "        pm.expect(p).to.have.property('actions');",
                  "        pm.expect(p.actions).to.be.an('array');",
                  "    });",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"budi.santoso@ikibisnis.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Password@123\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Login dengan email dan password. Token JWT akan otomatis tersimpan ke variable `access_token`.\n\n**Error cases:**\n- `401` — Email atau password salah\n- `401` — Akun dinonaktifkan\n- `429` — Rate limit (5 request/menit)"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 — Login berhasil",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
                "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"budi.santoso@ikibisnis.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Password@123\"\n}" },
                "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/login", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "login"] }
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"statusCode\": 200,\n  \"message\": \"Login berhasil\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"accessToken\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...\",\n    \"expiresIn\": 86400,\n    \"user\": {\n      \"id\": \"uuid-here\",\n      \"fullName\": \"Budi Santoso\",\n      \"email\": \"budi.santoso@ikibisnis.com\",\n      \"roleId\": \"uuid-role\",\n      \"roleName\": \"Admin\",\n      \"gender\": \"male\",\n      \"isActive\": true,\n      \"lastLoginAt\": \"2026-03-06T08:00:00.000Z\",\n      \"permissions\": [\n        { \"feature\": \"dashboard\",              \"actions\": [\"read\"] },\n        { \"feature\": \"user_management_roles\",  \"actions\": [\"read\", \"write\", \"update\", \"delete\"] },\n        { \"feature\": \"user_management_users\",  \"actions\": [\"read\", \"write\", \"update\", \"delete\"] },\n        { \"feature\": \"projects\",               \"actions\": [\"read\", \"write\", \"update\", \"delete\"] },\n        { \"feature\": \"penawaran\",              \"actions\": [\"read\", \"write\", \"update\", \"delete\"] },\n        { \"feature\": \"laporan_harian\",         \"actions\": [\"read\", \"write\", \"update\", \"delete\"] },\n        { \"feature\": \"laporan_neraca\",         \"actions\": [\"read\"] },\n        { \"feature\": \"laporan_laba_rugi\",      \"actions\": [\"read\"] },\n        { \"feature\": \"laporan_arus_kas\",       \"actions\": [\"read\"] },\n        { \"feature\": \"settings\",              \"actions\": [\"read\", \"write\", \"update\", \"delete\"] }\n      ]\n    }\n  }\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "401 — Email atau password salah",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
                "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"budi.santoso@ikibisnis.com\",\n  \"password\": \"WrongPass!\"\n}" },
                "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/login", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "login"] }
              },
              "status": "Unauthorized",
              "code": 401,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"statusCode\": 401,\n  \"message\": \"Email atau password salah.\"\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "401 — Akun tidak aktif",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
                "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"inactive@ikibisnis.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Password@123\"\n}" },
                "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/login", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "login"] }
              },
              "status": "Unauthorized",
              "code": 401,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"statusCode\": 401,\n  \"message\": \"Akun Anda telah dinonaktifkan. Hubungi administrator.\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "📁 Role",
      "description": "Manajemen Role. Semua endpoint membutuhkan JWT token dan permission `user_management_roles`.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. Create Role — Admin (semua akses)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.success && res.data && res.data.id) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('role_id', res.data.id);",
                  "    console.log('✅ role_id tersimpan:', res.data.id);",
                  "}",
                  "pm.test('Status 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "pm.test('Response success true', () => pm.expect(res.success).to.be.true);",
                  "pm.test('Data memiliki id', () => pm.expect(res.data).to.have.property('id'));",
                  "pm.test('Nama sesuai', () => pm.expect(res.data.name).to.eql('Admin'));",
                  "pm.test('Permissions tidak kosong', () => pm.expect(res.data.permissions).to.have.length.above(0));"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Admin\",\n  \"description\": \"Administrator dengan akses penuh ke seluruh fitur sistem\",\n  \"badgeColor\": \"#DC2626\",\n  \"permissions\": [\n    { \"feature\": \"dashboard\",                \"actions\": [\"read\"] },\n    { \"feature\": \"user_management_roles\",    \"actions\": [\"read\", \"write\", \"update\", \"delete\"] },\n    { \"feature\": \"user_management_users\",    \"actions\": [\"read\", \"write\", \"update\", \"delete\"] },\n    { \"feature\": \"projects\",                 \"actions\": [\"read\", \"write\", \"update\", \"delete\"] },\n    { \"feature\": \"penawaran\",                \"actions\": [\"read\", \"write\", \"update\", \"delete\"] },\n    { \"feature\": \"laporan_harian\",           \"actions\": [\"read\", \"write\", \"update\", \"delete\"] },\n    { \"feature\": \"laporan_neraca\",           \"actions\": [\"read\"] },\n    { \"feature\": \"laporan_laba_rugi\",        \"actions\": [\"read\"] },\n    { \"feature\": \"laporan_arus_kas\",         \"actions\": [\"read\"] },\n    { \"feature\": \"settings\",                 \"actions\": [\"read\", \"write\", \"update\", \"delete\"] }\n  ]\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/roles",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "roles"]
            },
            "description": "Membuat role Admin dengan akses penuh.\n\n**Permission dibutuhkan:** `user_management_roles` → `write`\n\n**Response 403** jika role Anda tidak punya akses write ke user_management_roles."
          },
          "response": [
