              "path": ["api", "v1", "roles"],
              "query": [{ "key": "page", "value": "1" }, { "key": "limit", "value": "10" }]
            },
            "description": "## SystemFeature\n\n| Feature Key | Menu |\n|---|---|\n| `dashboard` | Dashboard |\n| `user_management_roles` | User Management → Roles |\n| `user_management_users` | User Management → Users |\n| `projects` | Projects |\n| `penawaran` | Penawaran |\n| `laporan_harian` | Laporan Harian |\n| `laporan_neraca` | Laporan Neraca |\n| `laporan_laba_rugi` | Laporan Laba Rugi |\n| `laporan_arus_kas` | Laporan Arus Kas |\n| `settings` | Settings |\n\n## FeatureAction\n\n| Action | Endpoint yang dijaga |\n|---|---|\n| `read` | GET (list & detail) |\n| `write` | POST (create) |\n| `update` | PUT, PATCH |\n| `delete` | DELETE |\n\n## Permission Matrix Endpoint\n\n| Endpoint | Feature | Action |\n|---|---|---|\n| GET /roles | user_management_roles | read |\n| GET /roles/:id | user_management_roles | read |\n| POST /roles | user_management_roles | write |\n| PUT /roles/:id | user_management_roles | update |\n| PATCH /roles/:id/toggle-status | user_management_roles | update |\n| DELETE /roles/:id | user_management_roles | delete |\n| GET /users | user_management_users | read |\n| GET /users/:id | user_management_users | read |\n| POST /users | user_management_users | write |\n| PUT /users/:id | user_management_users | update |\n| PATCH /users/:id/change-password | user_management_users | update |\n| PATCH /users/:id/toggle-status | user_management_users | update |\n| DELETE /users/:id | user_management_users | delete |\n\n## Error Codes\n\n| Code | Penyebab |\n|---|---|\n| 401 | Token tidak ada / expired / user nonaktif |\n| 403 | Token valid tapi permission tidak cukup |\n| 403 | Role dinonaktifkan (isActive = false) |"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
